Hi, Saul. How're you doin'?

02:57.911 --> 03:00.209
Beverly, it's so nice to see you.

03:00.280 --> 03:02.805
- Hey, Mommy.
- % Help is on the way%

03:02.916 --> 03:06.010
- % Ohh, He's on His way%
- % Hold on%

03:06.086 --> 03:10.750
That's my mom. The Lord
blessed her with the gift of song.

03:10.824 --> 03:13.622
She's been singing
in this church her whole life.

03:13.694 --> 03:16.060
- % Say, He may not come%
- % He may not come%

03:16.129 --> 03:18.256
