- % When you want Him%

03:18.332 --> 03:19.924
% But He's right on time%

03:20.000 --> 03:22.127
- % But He'll be right there%
- % He'll be%

03:22.202 --> 03:26.195
- % On time%
- % He'll be on time%

03:26.273 --> 03:29.299
Her father used to be
the reverend here.

03:29.376 --> 03:33.813
But he's not anymore.
My daddy is.

03:33.881 --> 03:37.044
That's him...
the one holding his head.

03:37.117 --> 03:40.814
He's not looking too happy...

03:40.921 --> 03:44.823
which is sort of how
this whole story happened.

03:44.892 --> 03:46.917
- % Help is on the way, say%
